metadata.name: "Expresso cafe" (Coffe shop in State of México)
metadata.description:
" I took this photo when I was walking at night through the center of San Cristóbal, a central place for the inhabitants of Ecatepec de Morelos when I saw this cafe, the photo fails to represent the warm vibe that having a coffee represents inside the place that takes you to a garden since it is only the entrance but it does represent the street vibe of the downtown area "

Calle Benito Juárez Nte 5A, San Cristóbal Centro, 55000 Ecatepec de Morelos, Méx.
